  "id": "RAW_212ea34a",
  "title": "强化学习教父重出江湖， 生成式 AI 的时代要结束了？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652642887&idx=3&sn=a249244679bc3ab1be1f79cacbfb839b",
  "date": "2025-11-07 04:24:00",
  "author": "新智元",
